{"tid":450180,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）性格不合係唔係注定要分手？","createTime":"2017-10-28T02:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T13:46:57.000Z","uid":140024,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c43a5bfb5fb759f28ec9161f3508ddf05ef4dce8","tid":450180,"uid":140024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:31:26.000Z","msg":"我同男朋友一齊差唔多兩年，啱啱一齊嘅時候好sweet，佢對我好好<br />\n直到一年前開始好多嘈交，最近，佢突然同我講不如分開<br />\n我當然崩潰晒，問佢點解，佢話淡左<br />\n我覺得，感情當中一定會經歷淡左呢個問題，所以我唔肯分，佢都勉強同返我一起<br />\n但係我都仲係好唔開心，佢無時無刻提住叫我忘記佢，少少事就話不如分開（兩日講一次）<br />\n我好辛苦，唔知道應該點做，好冇安全感，日日喊<br />\n想請教下連登各位巴打，男人做到咁，其實係咪唔愛，冇可能再一齊落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3d3d861b444db8bdfaf0bca604fa93e65d9866","tid":450180,"uid":135390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:32:59.000Z","msg":"認真既<br />\n勉強冇結果<br />\n<br />\n利申 試過"},{"pid":"683d4c3434c91a3fcae2e7b9b26c3c041c20a469","tid":450180,"uid":140024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真既<br />\n勉強冇結果<br />\n<br />\n利申 試過</blockquote><br />\n我都知，但係我只係想再試下<br />\n我問佢，係咪已經唔愛我<br />\n佢話係淡左，唔係唔愛，但係已經唔想用力咁愛我<br />\n我只係想努力等佢再一次愛上我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706935deba28be4fe18e15159eda9f91ef2500f3","tid":450180,"uid":139828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:35:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38a3a1d18aa0cbc3cf400ceb050bccad9abec732","tid":450180,"uid":54878,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:35:46.000Z","msg":"唔好喊，錯不在你<br />\n2日講一次分手，可以肯定佢已經厭咗你"},{"pid":"f13046b4e56eb74aa88c8f75cdcae3882dcb928d","tid":450180,"uid":151619,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"一直拖住大家無用 長痛不如短痛 其實咁耐都磨合唔到就無謂辛苦大家 其實遲早都分手"},{"pid":"26b54cd993c43e8c9021e5fe401e690309c23846","tid":450180,"uid":140024,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扑厭左?</blockquote><br />\n冇扑過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個係咪問題所在？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3022f9417352c25b4ce630b3806b05b6898fa0","tid":450180,"uid":140024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直拖住大家無用 長痛不如短痛 其實咁耐都磨合唔到就無謂辛苦大家 其實遲早都分手</blockquote><br />\n佢一直都係咁講，但係我真係好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6296acc99568dbfa586f3145473e94f9f90c859","tid":450180,"uid":56320,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"冇架啦<br />\n你依啲唔係叫性格不合<br />\n係對方唔愛你"},{"pid":"08073ba7eb69814a3d82b04d261d31656495cec4","tid":450180,"uid":140024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好喊，錯不在你<br />\n2日講一次分手，可以肯定佢已經厭咗你</blockquote><br />\n我錯在將所有心思放晒係佢身上，突然要我抽身過冇佢嘅日子<br />\n我諗下都崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d36778c7d6552410a48a0a27ce60f00b8048bf","tid":450180,"uid":89145,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:42:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7517db8158dcd6172bc2b158bef1d98ea21c8e7a","tid":450180,"uid":127508,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"嘈交嘈到個心都累，<br />\n無力再去愛，<br />\n一諗到繼續走落去，又要繼續磨合，<br />\n就唔想面對。<br />\n<br />\n佢對你嘅愛已經唔夠去接受你哋嘅磨合。<br />\n<br />\n無結果，注定分手，<br />\n一段死咗嘅愛情好難重燃到。"},{"pid":"8c2479b68a787ecc7fc25884986f5c0338316920","tid":450180,"uid":154533,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:44:05.000Z","msg":"其實有幾多人覺得自己既父母性格真係好合?"},{"pid":"d34ab180a8317e7aa3bf558e1e784a337d23d3bd","tid":450180,"uid":90128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:44:31.000Z","msg":"佢都做左決定要分開 你又何必苦苦堅持呢<br />\n大家都辛苦"},{"pid":"b970ff0d320748d4b4611bb870e0ac9384fe9483","tid":450180,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>扑厭左?</blockquote><br />\n冇扑過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個係咪問題所在？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f02adb8914c9b2e32a783709f4d82b85873fe3a7","tid":450180,"uid":140024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘈交嘈到個心都累，<br />\n無力再去愛，<br />\n一諗到繼續走落去，又要繼續磨合，<br />\n就唔想面對。<br />\n<br />\n佢對你嘅愛已經唔夠去接受你哋嘅磨合。<br />\n<br />\n無結果，注定分手，<br />\n一段死咗嘅愛情好難重燃到。</blockquote><br />\n但係我願意為佢變，講真，有幾多段感情真係可以由一齊到死嘅一刻都唔變質，一直都咁愛大家？<br />\n一齊得耐左，多嘅係感情同習慣"},{"pid":"fea1a7cac1d92184399600271ec0451bc6a2d53c","tid":450180,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>扑厭左?</blockquote><br />\n冇扑過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個係咪問題所在？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對厭左你啦"},{"pid":"5e5420a95186e786aa31bf13938421ebd87c06af","tid":450180,"uid":78252,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:47:17.000Z","msg":"已經唔係淡，係厭倦<br />\n討厭，想甩身既感覺<br />\n放手啦"},{"pid":"48ed341d75b655881bc9f884c7889be61d2a37e8","tid":450180,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:48:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嘈交嘈到個心都累，<br />\n無力再去愛，<br />\n一諗到繼續走落去，又要繼續磨合，<br />\n就唔想面對。<br />\n<br />\n佢對你嘅愛已經唔夠去接受你哋嘅磨合。<br />\n<br />\n無結果，注定分手，<br />\n一段死咗嘅愛情好難重燃到。</blockquote><br />\n但係我願意為佢變，講真，有幾多段感情真係可以由一齊到死嘅一刻都唔變質，一直都咁愛大家？<br />\n一齊得耐左，多嘅係感情同習慣</blockquote><br />\n願意為佢變點解當初又咁多交嘈"},{"pid":"181ae9354e23303dc4b72be8c47f9995f3d0ffbe","tid":450